<div class="pull-column-examples">
  <h2>Pull Column left</h2>
  {{#> pull-column direction="left"}}
    {{> pull-column__content}}
    {{> pull-column__pulled}}
  {{/pull-column}}

  <h2>Pull Column right</h2>
  {{#> pull-column direction="right"}}
    {{> pull-column__pulled}}
    {{> pull-column__content}}
  {{/pull-column}}

  <h2>Re-order items for mobile</h2>
  {{#> pull-column direction="left" modifier="reorder-items"}}
    {{> pull-column__content}}
    {{> pull-column__pulled}}
  {{/pull-column}}

  <h2>Pull background</h2>
  {{#> pull-column direction="left" modifier="pulled-background"}}
    {{> pull-column__content}}
    {{> pull-column__pulled}}
  {{/pull-column}}
</div>

{{#*inline "pull-column"}}
  <div class="pull-column pull-column--{{direction}} pull-column--{{modifier}} u-pv-large u-mb-large">
    {{> @partial-block }}
  </div>
{{/inline}}

{{#*inline "pull-column__content"}}
  <div class="pull-column__content">
    <div class="example-content">
      Consectetur quaerat at mollitia suscipit voluptatibus?
    </div>
  </div>
{{/inline}}

{{#*inline "pull-column__pulled"}}
  <div class="pull-column__pulled">
    <div class="example-content">
      Eligendi neque reprehenderit fugit odit molestiae eveniet Soluta quia doloribus nemo officiis veritatis Fugiat nemo minima nulla omnis molestias!
    </div>
  </div>
{{/inline}}
